title: Maasila unmai Kadhale Lyrics Alibabavum 40 Thirudargalum

Maasila unmai Kadhale Lyrics From Alibabavum 40 Thirudargalum

Maasila unmai kadhale
Maarumo selvam
Vandha podhile

Pesum vaarthai
Unmai thaanaa
Pedaiyai eikka 
Neengal podum
Vesama ?

Kannile minnum
Kadhale 
Kandumaa sandhegam
Endhan meedhile

Nenjile neengidaadhu
Konjum inbamey.
Nilaikkumaa indha
Endha naalumey.
